Description:
    Generate Metronic new view for nested resource (e.g., issues/employees).

Example:
    rails g views:metronic:new issues/employees --namespace=protected --force

Options:
    --namespace=protected   Namespace for views

Notes:
    - Assumes nested routes exist like:
      protected_employee_issues_path(parent) (create)
      new_protected_employee_issue_path(parent) (new)
    - The generator renders a page header with back action and a form partial.